    <name>Distance and Social Presence​</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{235}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.15,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:0}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;It is important to bring back some of the &lt;strong&gt;“&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;social presence&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;”&lt;/strong&gt; that may be missing when your &amp;nbsp;learners&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;are not&amp;nbsp;physically located with their peers. Social presence is defined as the “ability of learners to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;project themselves socially and emotionally as well as their ability to perceive other learners as ‘real&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;people.’” &lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9888@$" target="_blank"&gt;(Boston et al, 2010)&lt;/a&gt;. By building social presence into your course,&amp;nbsp;you can create a more&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;inviting, friendly, welcoming environment that can help put adult learners at ease, especially if they&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;are returning to school after a long absence and already have some reservations about the journey&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;ahead&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9888@$" target="_blank"&gt;(Lee et al., 2021)&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{238}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.15,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:0}"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Here are some ideas for how to support the development of a social presence which are expanded&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;on in subsequent sections:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul role="list"&gt;&lt;li data-margin="1085" data-aria-posinset="1" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{241}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1085,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:12,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Help learners create a profile&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-margin="1085" data-aria-posinset="2" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{244}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1085,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Help learners make a video&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-margin="1085" data-aria-posinset="3" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{247}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1085,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Showcase practical skills&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-margin="1085" data-aria-posinset="4" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{250}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1085,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Guide online discussions&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{253}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.15,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:0}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider%20wave.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
